          Design & Concept
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-black dark:text-white col-span-4 md:col-span-6">
          From hypothesis to prototype, I design and test intuitive experiences that evolve through iteration and validation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Item -->
